  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"display: inline-block;text-indent: 2em;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100027689\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4637053087757313\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"923\" style=\"left: 0px;top: 0px;width: 416px;background-color: transparent;height: 193px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Z300vPwLQkmaScu1ezCwt0PQibgxFAicAicPpD2o9xa9VsAAhVCoMicCDe4hH9AvYlItgNCos4Upd4YtMyYtYXgk0A/0?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"77.60532150776054\" data-cropx2=\"1000\" data-cropy1=\"128.6031042128603\" data-cropy2=\"556.5410199556541\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21845c50&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZ300vPwLQkmaScu1ezCwt0PQibgxFAicAicNqLZHvia2pMgDibsuMAsF9FohssnWWM62TtW1LhK01Conmk29YwnWiaHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m8im\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">继轻量级强化学习（RL）框架&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">slime</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;在社区中悄然流行并支持了包括 GLM-4.6 在内的大量 Post-training 流水线与 MoE 训练任务之后</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">LMSYS 团队</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">正式推出&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Miles</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">——</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">一个专为企业级大规模 MoE 训练及生产环境工作负载设计的强化学习框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m167k\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Miles 从 slime 分叉（fork）而来，在继承其轻量级与高可定制性基因的基础上，针对新一代硬件（如 GB300）与大规模 MoE 进行了深度优化。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">它引入了 Infrastructure-level 的&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">True On-Policy（严格在线策略）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">投机训练（Speculative Training）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;以及更极致的显存管理机制，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">旨在为追求高可靠性与大规模部署的团队提供流畅且可控的 RL 训练体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4mr09\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">千里之行，始于足下。Miles 的发布标志着 LMSYS 团队在构建生产级 AI 基础设施道路上迈出的关键一步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m219l\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:24px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi6roke086q\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rokeuqhu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Z Highlights：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m189b\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">True On-Policy（严格在线策略）：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">为了消除训练与推理之间的微小偏差，Miles 采用了基于基础设施的方法，结合 Flash Attention 3 和 DeepGEMM，实现了训练与推理的严格一致性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m21x3\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">引入 MTP Online Training 的投机采样：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;针对 RL 场景，Miles 在训练过程中对 Draft Model 进行在线 SFT，解决了分布偏移问题，实现了 25%+ 的 Rollout 加速。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4mr9y\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">极致的显存优化：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Miles 实施了包括 NCCL 显存余量控制、部分 Offloading 及 Host 峰值内存节省在内的一系列改进，大幅减少大规模 MoE 训练中的 OOM 风险。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m5w5\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:24px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">从 slime 出发：轻量与模块化的传承</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m21fk\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Miles 的起点源于 slime——一个在开源社区与 LMSYS 内部备受推崇的轻量级框架。slime 因其优雅的设计原则，已成为众多模型科学家探索算法的首选工具。Miles 完整继承了这些核心优势：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4mj0d\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">原生高性能：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">对 SGLang 和 Megatron 的全栈优化提供原生支持，紧跟推理与训练框架的快速迭代。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m105b\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">清晰的模块化设计：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;算法（Algorithm）、数据（Data）、采样（Rollout）与评估（Eval）四大组件完全解耦。研究人员仅需极少的代码修改即可插入新的 Agent 类型或奖励函数。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m142q\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">对模型科学家友好：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;所有抽象层均保持高可读性。算法研究员无需触碰底层代码即可修改重要性采样（Importance Sampling）或 Loss 动态，且框架提供了独立的 Inference-only 和 Training-only 调试模式，便于快速诊断。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1nd6\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Miles 的诞生，正是基于 LMSYS 和 SGLang 社区的真实反馈，是将开放协作转化为工程实践的典范。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m20rv\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:24px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">迈向生产级：Miles 的核心技术突破</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1tr3\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">在保留 slime 灵活性的同时，LMSYS 团队在 Miles 中注入了针对企业级应用和新一代硬件（GB300）的“强心剂”。以下是 Miles 近期实施的关键技术升级：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m11qj\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Infrastructure-level 的 True On-Policy</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4moz\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">为了追求极致的算法正确性，Miles 除了支持现有的确定性（Deterministic）采样外，还进一步通过 kernel 层面的优化实现了</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">True On-Policy</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">训练与推理之间的 mismatch 被精确地降至零。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1yok\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">具体实现上，团队利用了&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Flash Attention 3</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">DeepGEMM</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">以及来自 Thinking Machines Lab 的 Batch invariant kernels，并结合 torch compile 技术。此外，团队还对训练和推理过程中的数值运算细节进行了严格对齐，确保了结果的位级一致性（bit-wise consistence）。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1ws\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100027691\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"left: 0px;top: 0px;width: 100%;height: 395px;background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=913552a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZ300vPwLQkmaScu1ezCwt0PQibgxFAicAiceBibr4vrcggdtWAiblIF1XAMHZbgp29gNJC2MHgkqRR7SFh9XQibiadgibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m10ts\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:24px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">大规模 MoE 显存优化</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m8bi\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">为了在不触发 OOM（显存溢出）的前提下最大限度地榨取 GPU 性能，Miles 进行了一系列显存管理升级：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m16l7\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">引入了传播机制以规避良性 OOM 导致的错误；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m24u0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">实现了显存余量机制（Memory Margin）以修复 NCCL 导致的 OOM；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1vjk\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">修复了 FSDP 中的额外显存占用问题；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4mnee\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">支持基于 Move 的部分 Offloading 以及 Host 端峰值内存节省策略。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m284\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:24px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">引入在线 SFT 的投机采样</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4my6o\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">在强化学习场景中，如果 Draft Model（草稿模型）保持冻结，它将无法跟随 Target Model（目标模型）的策略变化，导致接受长度（Accept Length）下降，从而削弱加速效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1y57\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">为此，Miles 创新性地在 RL 过程中对 Draft Model 进行</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">在线 SFT（Online SFT）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1w99\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">性能提升：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;相比于冻结 MTP（Medusa-Tree-Pruning）基线，该方法实现了&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">25% 以上</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;的 Rollout 加速，尤其在训练后期效果显著。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1187\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">功能完备：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;支持带 Sequence Packing 和 Context Parallel (CP) 的 MTP；处理了 Loss Mask 的边缘情况；实现了 LM Head/Embedding 的梯度隔离，以及 Megatron 与 SGLang 之间的权重同步。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4mzi2\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100027690\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"left: 0px;top: 0px;width: 100%;height: 480px;background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"806\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d0665fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZ300vPwLQkmaScu1ezCwt0PQibgxFAicAicLxkKBfAktYuOESmicxJOMsw1WQiayjZbeRMnaQsSP3ZZxP5QIQYVjFCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m11kq\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">其它工程改进</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4maxb\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">增强 FSDP 后端：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;提升了大规模分布式训练的稳定性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1v72\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">独立部署 Rollout：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;允许 Rollout 子系统脱离框架独立部署，适应更灵活的集群调度。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1yea\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">调试工具集：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;新增了更多监控指标、Post-hoc 分析器及增强型 Profiler。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m16l6\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">数学形式化验证：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;提供了包含 SFT/RL 脚本的 Lean 语言形式化数学示例。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m106b\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:24px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">未来路线图与社区愿景</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1fpg\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">LMSYS 团队表示，Miles 的发布仅仅是一个开始。为了进一步支持企业级 RL 训练，未来的开发路线图包括：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1wlg\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">新硬件支持：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;在 GB300 等下一代硬件上运行大规模 MoE RL 的示例。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4mign\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">多模态训练：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;扩展对 Multi-modal 模型的支持。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1fov\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Rollout 加速：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;兼容 SGLang Spec v2 以获得更高性能；推进 EAGLE3 及 Multi-spec layer 等更先进的投机训练技术。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1qlr\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">弹性训练：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;实现针对大规模异步训练的计算资源均衡分配，以及对 GPU 故障的弹性容错（Elastic to GPU failures）。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1at1\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Miles 的存在离不开 slime 作者群及广泛的 SGLang/RL 社区的贡献。LMSYS 团队诚邀研究人员、初创公司及企业团队试用 Miles，共同打造高效、可靠的强化学习生产环境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1t4p\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-style: italic;\">原文链接：<a href=\"https://lmsys.org/blog/2025-11-19-miles/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lmsys.org/blog/2025-11-19-miles/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6rcu4m1t4p\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi6skyv51lzl\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi6skyva7np\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">Z Tech 将继续提供更多关于人工智能、全球化市场、机器人技术等领域的独家技术分析与学术Talk。我们诚邀对未来充满憧憬的您加入我们的Phd/Reseachers的实名社群！，与我们共同分享、学习、成长。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "LMSYS 团队发布 Miles 框架，专为大规模 MoE 强化学习训练及生产环境设计，提供严格在线策略、投机训练和极致显存优化。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "LMSYS 团队发布 Miles 框架，专为大规模 MoE 强化学习训练及生产环境设计，提供严格在线策略、投机训练和极致显存优化。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 LMSYS 团队推出的 Miles 强化学习框架，它是轻量级框架 slime 的升级版，专为企业级大规模 MoE 模型训练和生产环境工作负载优化。Miles 继承了 slime 的轻量级、高可定制性、原生高性能和模块化设计等核心优势。在此基础上，Miles 引入了基础设施级的严格在线策略（True On-Policy），通过结合 Flash Attention 3、DeepGEMM 和 torch compile 等技术，彻底消除了训练与推理之间的偏差，确保位级一致性。针对强化学习场景，Miles 创新性地在训练过程中对 Draft Model 进行在线 SFT，解决了分布偏移问题，实现了 25%+的 Rollout 加速。此外，它还实施了一系列极致显存优化措施，如 NCCL 显存余量控制、部分 Offloading 等，显著降低了大规模 MoE 训练中的 OOM 风险。文章最后展望了 Miles 在未来对新硬件、多模态训练和弹性训练的支持，旨在为追求高可靠性和大规模部署的团队提供流畅可控的 RL 训练体验。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Miles 实现 Infrastructure-level 的 True On-Policy，确保训练与推理严格一致性。",
      "explanation": "通过结合 Flash Attention 3、DeepGEMM 和 torch compile 等底层技术，从基础设施层面消除了训练与推理之间的微小偏差，达到位级一致性，极大提升了算法的正确性和可靠性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入在线 SFT 的投机采样，有效解决分布偏移并加速 Rollout。",
      "explanation": "在强化学习过程中对 Draft Model 进行在线 SFT，使其策略能跟随 Target Model 变化，有效避免了分布偏移导致的加速效果下降，实现了 25%以上的 Rollout 加速。"
    },
    {
      "point": "实施极致显存优化，显著降低大规模 MoE 训练的 OOM 风险。",
      "explanation": "通过传播机制规避 OOM、NCCL 显存余量控制、FSDP 显存占用修复及基于 Move 的部分 Offloading 等策略，最大限度地榨取 GPU 性能，解决了大规模 MoE 训练中的关键瓶颈。"
    },
    {
